    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方粉丝QQ群：594878167</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的筹码是金币，你的赌注是自由。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/c22e8492ba287ee545ccc1b7f724e957.poster.avif?t=1771946297\" aria-label=\"黑色夹克的机械变体。\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/c22e8492ba287ee545ccc1b7f724e957.webm?t=1771946297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>地狱黑杰克</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是一款融合21点规则的roguelite牌组构建游戏。你不仅要计算点数、管理风险，还要通过卡牌效果、神器组合与角色能力，在每一局中生存并壮大。你能攒够船资，击败摆渡人，逃出这个永不放行的地狱吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/2cfa5d73929cfde116bb3345fca72c0f.poster.avif?t=1771946297\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/2cfa5d73929cfde116bb3345fca72c0f.webm?t=1771946297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的21点牌组构建</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构建致命的牌组——从经典花色到扭曲卡牌，吸收、洞察、燃烧、交换……打出超乎想象的组合，逆转劣势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觉醒卡牌获得强大负面或正面效果，探索多种卡牌协同效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度变体博弈——Blackjack多种特殊效果，觉醒卡牌带来高风险高回报。每一次选择，都可能彻底改变你的游戏方式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操纵并改变规则，每一步都是你决胜的关键。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/be68730a8712d1d067240637dcf1757c.poster.avif?t=1771946297\" aria-label=\"一套包含不同花色的卡片序列：红心、方块、黑桃、梅花，以及新增的花色：火焰与圣杯。\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/be68730a8712d1d067240637dcf1757c.webm?t=1771946297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>隐晦深邃的情感叙事</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与充满故事的亡魂对局——熟悉他们的作战风格与诅咒机制，找到破局的关键。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑暗诗意氛围：手绘艺术、忧郁配乐、充满隐喻的文本。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过卡牌揭示他们的过去、痛苦与希望，解开牌局背后的黑暗过往。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/59784315202ba7e14136bd2e93a2fc89.poster.avif?t=1771946297\" aria-label=\"你在游戏中遇到的不同BOSS的剪影。\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/59784315202ba7e14136bd2e93a2fc89.webm?t=1771946297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富的挑战和收集</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索随机领域——穿越外层世界、短暂之地、内层世界，直至逃离地狱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商店交易、神器收集、挑战解锁，层层推进你的旅程。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难度逐步叠加，失败只是下一次更强的开始。数百张卡牌、数十种神器、多种变化，确保每次旅程都独一无二。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/b461d2b025cb4fe3784e6c7c1f7a2166.poster.avif?t=1771946297\" aria-label=\"在整个游戏过程中可进行卡组构建\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/b461d2b025cb4fe3784e6c7c1f7a2166.webm?t=1771946297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>穿上你的黑夹克，面对你的过去</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>或者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>永远留在这里。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>马上添加愿望单！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/cc8f10096fb1c1e01577bb0dcc5aa6db.poster.avif?t=1771946297\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100370/extras/cc8f10096fb1c1e01577bb0dcc5aa6db.webm?t=1771946297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
